Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.69,0:24:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La prossima volta faremo scacco al re!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.38,0:24:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspetta, non ancora!
